    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a small drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>to a pot with a lid over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong> and the<strong> sliced spring onion whites</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
