            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), <strong>grated carrot </strong>and <strong>sliced radishes</strong> to a bowl with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside to pickle until serving – these are your<strong> quick-pickled vegetables</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1705075213921-x200.jpg",
