            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the fable pulled mushrooms have crisped, add your <strong>mirin</strong>, <strong>tamari soy sauce</strong>, <strong>remaining ginger & garlic paste </strong>and 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\"><span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tsp]</span> [4 tsp]</span><strong> sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until coated – this is your <strong>Fable pulled mushroom teriyaki</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>mangetout</strong> to a large bowl, cover with <strong>boiled water</strong> and set aside to soften</p><p>Drain the <strong>mangetout</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1705075221046-x200.jpg",
