            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1705075221046-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Fable pulled mushroom teriyaki</strong> over the<strong> garlic rice</strong>, with the<strong> quick-pickled vegetables </strong>and <strong>mangetout</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion greens</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
